<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3920.3.8>
    bibo:endPage "492" ;
    bibo:issue "3" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "488" ;
    bibo:volume "3920" ;
    dc:creator "Háva, Jiří; Kadej, Marcin" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Description of a new species of Anthrenus Geoffroy 1762, with a key to species from Nepal" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236620> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.236620>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 11. Anthrenus (Helocerus) cechovskyi sp. n.: 1. habitus of male (dorsal, holotype); 2 – 3. habitus of females (dorsal, paratypes); 4. abdominal ventrites I – V (holotype); 5. abdominal ventrites I – V (paratype); 6. male antenna (left, holotype); 7. female antenna (left, paratype); 8. abdominal segment IX (holotype); 9. male genitalia (ventral, holotype); 10. pygiudium (holotype); 11. galea with lacinia (holotype)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/236620/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

